    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> meaty pulled mushrooms</strong> to the dish with the <strong>onion quarters</strong> and<strong> crushed garlic</strong></p><p>Cook for 2 min or until very lightly browned</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1679419372515-x200.jpg",
