            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pour your<strong> red wine vinegar</strong> over the<strong> sliced onion</strong> and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong></p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p><p>Tip: Check the stew halfway and give everything a good stir!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
