        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the stew is almost done, add your <strong>naan[s]</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) and put the tray[s] in the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p><p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong>, discard the liquid</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
